{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find your way through the expansive domains of the Afterlife by using your soul as a grappling hook in this tight, non-linear, physics-based platformer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383610/extras/little_banner.png?t=1733925135\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Swing </strong>your way through hundreds of hand-crafted platforming challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore</strong> the seasons of the Afterlife in your own way in a branching world inspired by classic metroidvanias </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Meet </strong>a colorful cast of characters and help them through their journeys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Adjust </strong>the difficulty level through a series of assist options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenge </strong>yourself through the Night, a brutal parallel world only for the boldest little souls</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The grapple allows for careful and thoughtful movements, as well as quick and risky tricks, making up a toolkit that feels deeply expressive from beginner to pro. Explore the world in your own pace and find your place within the Afterlife.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383610/extras/swinging.gif?t=1733925135\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733925135","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383610/page.bg.jpg?t=1733925135","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s